{"tid":182193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國脫歐，歐盟以直布羅陀話事權要脅英國","createTime":"2017-04-01T06:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T21:53:39.000Z","uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5529ea18aada67b576703061da687bcf89d1cd43","tid":182193,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:48:43.000Z","msg":"歐盟主席圖斯克（Donald Tusk）周五提出英國脫歐談判指引，但當中指出如無西班牙同意，歐盟與英國日後關係的協議，例如自由貿易協議，將不適用於英西兩國有主權爭議的直布羅陀，<span style=\"color: red;\">變相讓西班牙可用自貿協議作籌碼，逼英國把直布羅陀交給西班牙。</span>消息令英國政壇震驚及憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲聯盟公布與英國的脫歐談判指引，列明若果英國與西班牙不能達成共識，歐盟與英國的協議將不適用於英國屬地直布羅陀。<br />\n<br />\n直布羅陀首席部長皮卡爾多認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟建議西班牙可介入英國脫歐後的直布羅陀事務</span>，屬不必要及帶歧視性。他又批評，西班牙企圖透過歐洲議會取得狹隘的政治利益。<br />\n<br />\n英國與西班牙就直布羅陀一直有主權爭議，預料歐盟有關談判指引將引起英國強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有直布羅陀官員表明，憂慮西班牙會阻止直布羅陀被納入英國與歐盟之間協議範圍內。"},{"pid":"fadddcde0e208fdde79f7d4804ddc88ec17ccaf3","tid":182193,"uid":39167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"黑社會歐盟版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入得唔出得"},{"pid":"dafbe3d25f0c8ec69f8e70548c207c2c1af2edfd","tid":182193,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"西班牙/歐盟=中國<br />\n直布羅陀=香港<br />\n英國=英國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2692234274dfd84b76b6ba6978ca3e4aa722eaa","tid":182193,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08b38dc83b3bfc5ef1e1e6bc590fcb6d41fd5f2e","tid":182193,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>西班牙/歐盟=中國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直布羅陀=香港</span><br />\n英國=英國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好侮辱直布羅陀<br />\n人地一直都好親英唔想主權移交"},{"pid":"82b8334c4a993417882728b6b2de93e6c2d65c00","tid":182193,"uid":72694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"睇WIKI先知直布羅陀D人係想留係歐盟<br />\n唔怪得比人要脅"},{"pid":"6191c8729434b31130ac144a51f7158e9792fc5b","tid":182193,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑社會歐盟版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入得唔出得</blockquote><br />\n歐盟仆街唔係第一日先知啦"},{"pid":"d432d33651f13638424eda253332718934768d9d","tid":182193,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇WIKI先知直布羅陀D人係想留係歐盟<br />\n唔怪得比人要脅</blockquote><br />\n不過直布羅陀人唔想併入西班牙呢, 連比西班牙共同管治都唔想<br />\n02年97%人投維持做英國屬地既一部份, <br />\n直布羅陀人同蘇格蘭唔同<br />\n佢地對英國歸屬感好強, 同長久以黎對西班牙係有種抗拒心(因為西班牙成日擺佢地上枱)<br />\n就算想做歐盟人都好我唔覺得西班牙有乜機會可能透過公投方式拎到直布羅陀<br />\n而直英國接割直布羅陀比西班牙就更加無可能<br />\n所以今次EU真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5547a79215ab30bb3b0fe5e33e5f89a7f6cb69","tid":182193,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西班牙/歐盟=中國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直布羅陀=香港</span><br />\n英國=英國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好侮辱直布羅陀<br />\n人地一直都好親英唔想主權移交</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個等號係身處既狀況，<br />\n而家直布羅陀就好似當年香港咁，<br />\n畀英國同歐盟/西班牙踢黎踢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faaa77f63939ffcf5d81e73558a0f9ff7112759","tid":182193,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"蘇格蘭直布羅陀變一個國家，持bno者可以入籍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nff中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f262e9ccf532f267178fb87c0c2f007fda4c034","tid":182193,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:24:34.000Z","msg":"無左eu 咪返去以前果種歐洲平衡勢力外交, 英國由幾百年黎強果方變左弱果方<br />\n如果英聯邦同盟搞唔到更緊密合作, 英國都有排煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要加多個蘇獨factor"},{"pid":"76731d8fdc19188cda41324cc59461393ad9ae08","tid":182193,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西班牙/歐盟=中國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直布羅陀=香港</span><br />\n英國=英國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好侮辱直布羅陀<br />\n人地一直都好親英唔想主權移交</blockquote><br />\n當年香港都大把人親英<br />\n唔係洗乜97走晒一堆精英，留番依家堆廢老係香港？"},{"pid":"64497de6b6488c28431a31d2494e05d2cf8c99df","tid":182193,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西班牙/歐盟=中國<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">直布羅陀=香港</span><br />\n英國=英國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好侮辱直布羅陀<br />\n人地一直都好親英唔想主權移交</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個等號係身處既狀況，<br />\n而家直布羅陀就好似當年香港咁，<br />\n畀英國同歐盟/西班牙踢黎踢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係自己既未來無自己話事權，<br />\n自己既將來由英國倫敦政府同<br />\n歐盟/西班牙決定呢一方面，<br />\n可以話同當年香港好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b60204baaba735ea383784b35d4a17cb9b5db9","tid":182193,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"歐盟真係好仆街 脫歐咪脫歐<br />\n好黎好去 洗唔洗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown